<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Ride Share!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
        padding: 20px 10px;
      }
      .feature {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .top-header {
        background-color: #000;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
      .feature-icon {
        width: 150px;
        height: 150px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .flex {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
      }
      .icon {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }
      .bg-black {
        margin-top: 10px;
        background-color: #000;
        border-radius: 20px;
        color: #fff;
      }
      .mx-2 {
        margin: 0 20px;
      }
      /* Add more styles as needed */
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img
        src="../../public/images/logo.png"
        alt="Publish Ride"
        width="70px"
        style="margin-bottom: 20px"
      />
      <div class="top-header feature">
        <img
          src="../../public/images/Illustration.png"
          alt="Publish Ride"
          class="feature-icon"
        />
        <h2 style="color: #fff">Welcome to Ride Share!</h2>
        <p style="color: #fff">We are so happy to have you.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="text-align: center">Our Best Features</h2>
      <div class="feature flex bg-black">
        <img
          src="../../public/images/paper-plane.png"
          alt="Add Driver to Favorite"
          width="50"
          class="icon"
        />
        <div>
          <h2>Publish Ride</h2>
          <p>
            With the "Publish Ride" feature, you can easily share your upcoming
            journey with a wide audience. Whether you're planning a road trip, a
            bike ride, or a thrilling adventure, this feature allows you to make
            your travel plans public
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature flex bg-black">
        <div>
          <h2>Join Ride</h2>
          <p>
            Seamlessly connect drivers offering rides with passengers seeking
            cost-effective and eco-friendly transportation, fostering community
            and convenience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="../../public/images/connect.png"
          alt="Add Driver to Favorite"
          width="50"
          class="icon"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="feature flex bg-black">
        <img
          src="../../public/images/favorite.png"
          alt="Add Driver to Favorite"
          width="50"
          class="icon"
        />
        <div>
          <h2>Add Driver to Favorite</h2>
          <p>
            Our "Add Driver to Favorites" feature is designed to provide you
            with a seamless and convenient way to personalize your experience on
            our platform. Whether you're a rideshare user, delivery recipient,
            or simply want to remember specific drivers for future interactions
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2023 Ride Share. All rights reserved.</p>
        <img src="../../public/images/ints.png" alt="Instagram" class="mx-2" />
        <img src="../../public/images/fb.png" alt="Facebook" class="mx-2" />
        <img src="../../public/images/link.png" alt="LinkedIn" class="mx-2" />
        <img src="../../public/images/twiiter.png" alt="Twitter" class="mx-2" />
        <p>
          If you have any questions, feel free to message us at
          RideShare@email.com.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
